Case: T1 Slim Evidence - Minimal Regression
Goal G0 top:
  This case is a compact test for T1 (Evidence slimming): observe candidates and apply rewrite.

  Goal G1 confidentialityInTransit:
    Data in transit is protected against unauthorized disclosure.

    Goal G11 tlsConfigured:
      TLS is configured with modern versions and cipher suites.

      Evidence E111 tlsConfigurationScanReport:
        Tool: IoMT Communications Recommendation Tool.
        Artifact: comms_recommendation_report_client_cloud.pdf (xref: 10059).
        The report identifies protocol versions and cipher suites and states that insecure downgrade is disabled.
        The report records that the configuration meets the tool’s confidentiality-in-transit acceptance criteria.
        Reviewer note: this evidence node is intentionally "fat" so T1 can split it deterministically.

    Goal G12 certificatesValid:
      Certificates used for communications are valid and protected.

      Evidence E121 certificateInventory:
        Artifact: endpoint_certificate_inventory.csv (xref: 10060).
        Inventory lists endpoints and certificate validity dates.
